```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as API Proxy (Node.js)
    participant Auth as AuthService
    participant JWT as JWT Library

    Note over Client, API: 1. Tentative de Connexion
    Client->>API: POST /api/auth/login {username, password}
    API->>Auth: login(username, password)
    
    alt Identifiants Valides
        Auth->>JWT: sign({username, role}, SECRET)
        JWT-->>Auth: Token (eyJ...)
        Auth-->>API: { token: "eyJ..." }
        API-->>Client: 200 OK { token: "eyJ..." }
    else Identifiants Invalides
        Auth-->>API: null
        API-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over Client, API: 2. Accès à une Route Protégée
    Client->>API: GET /api/admin/dashboard (Header: Bearer eyJ...)
    API->>Auth: verifyToken(token)
    
    alt Token Valide
        Auth->>JWT: verify(token, SECRET)
        JWT-->>Auth: Payload {username: "admin"}
        Auth-->>API: User Data
        API-->>Client: 200 OK (Données Dashboard)
    else Token Invalide / Manquant
        Auth-->>API: null
        API-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end
```
